title: EntityLinker import not working
body:
Hi everyone, 

I'm unable to import the scispacy EntityLinker using the code:
```
import spacy
import scispacy

from scispacy.linking import EntityLinker
```

When I run this piece of code in the Jupyter lab, the cell does not run and probably the kernel dies or restarts. I'm not sure what exactly is happening. 

Details which might be useful:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40318353/121766015-acbe6f00-cb6c-11eb-8597-0594f5262ba7.png)
